    "body": "> It is 0 by default\r\n\r\nthis is the fetched block difficulty because difficulty is no longer used in POS, you should not rely on it: https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-4399\r\n\r\nsee also\r\n\r\n```\r\ncast rpc eth_getBlockByHash \"0x4558ab5459cc322d4516ff360158631bbbc32e50f4c1532229ac631f56731e91\" false --rpc-url $GOERLI_RPC_URL | jq\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
